    "English": "Advanced munition fragments, constructed to fit Universal Multi-Tool Standard 07/FF1.<br><br>Easily inserted into the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Boltcaster</span>, <span class=\"name name-technology\">Pulse Spitter</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">Scatter Blaster</span> via the Multi-Tool clip reloading system.",
