    "TencentChinese": "高级弹药碎片，符合通用多用途工具标准07/FF1。<br><br>可通过多用途工具弹匣装弹系统轻易插入<span class=\"name name-technology\">离子闪电发射器</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">脉冲喷射器</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">散射迸裂器</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "進階彈藥碎片，符合通用工具組標準 07/FF1。<br><br>能輕易透過工具組彈匣填充系統裝入<span class=\"name name-technology\">雷霆砲</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">脈衝槍</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">雙管霰彈槍</span>。"
